  <div class="sublist_thumbs"><h4><a href="http://www.npr.org/series/kitchen-window/">Kitchen Window</a></h4><div class="bucket img"><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/07/20/138513444/the-lighter-side-of-traditional-soviet-summer-fare"><img src="http://media.npr.org/assets/img/2011/07/19/sovietsummer_sq.jpg?t=1311171537&amp;s=11" alt="Flavors of the former empire are rooted in regional cuisine. But it's not all borscht and dumplings."/></a><div class="bucketblock"><h3><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/07/20/138513444/the-lighter-side-of-traditional-soviet-summer-fare">The Lighter Side Of Traditional Soviet Summer Fare</a></h3><p>Flavors of the former empire are rooted in regional cuisine. But it's not all borscht and dumplings.</p></div></div><div class="bucket img"><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/07/14/137794595/the-glorious-pasta-of-summer"><img src="http://media.npr.org/assets/img/2011/07/12/pastamain_sq.jpg?t=1310519803&amp;s=11" alt="Stay cool by dressing fun pasta shapes with a saute of peak-of-the-season vegetables and herbs."/></a><div class="bucketblock"><h3><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/07/14/137794595/the-glorious-pasta-of-summer">The Glorious Pasta Of Summer</a></h3><p>Stay cool by dressing fun pasta shapes with a saute of peak-of-the-season vegetables and herbs.</p></div></div><div class="bucket img"><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/07/06/137623588/fresh-feisty-arugula-more-than-a-salad-green"><img src="http://media.npr.org/assets/img/2011/07/05/arugulapizza_sq.jpg?t=1309886368&amp;s=11" alt="Arugula, aka &quot;rocket,&quot; takes meaty pizza, nutty quinoa and creamy pasta dishes to new heights."/></a><div class="bucketblock"><h3><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/07/06/137623588/fresh-feisty-arugula-more-than-a-salad-green">Fresh, Feisty Arugula: More Than A Salad Green</a></h3><p>Arugula, aka "rocket," takes meaty pizza, nutty quinoa and creamy pasta dishes to new heights.</p></div></div><div class="bucket img"><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/07/06/137472461/july-4-barbecue-from-americas-melting-pot"><img src="http://media.npr.org/assets/img/2011/06/28/bbqmainchorizoclams_sq.jpg?t=1309275914&amp;s=11" alt="Grilling in the U.S.A.: Hot dogs and burgers make way for chorizo, kalbi, yakitori, kebab and more."/></a><div class="bucketblock"><h3><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/07/06/137472461/july-4-barbecue-from-americas-melting-pot">July 4 Barbecue From America's Melting Pot</a></h3><p>Grilling in the U.S.A.: Hot dogs and burgers make way for chorizo, kalbi, yakitori, kebab and more.</p></div></div><div class="bucket img"><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/07/06/137219913/no-wheat-doesn-t-mean-no-noodles"><img src="http://media.npr.org/assets/img/2011/06/16/noodlesmain_sq.jpg?t=1308234829&amp;s=11" alt="For people who eat gluten-free, Asian rice noodles are the crossover stars. But they're not alone."/></a><div class="bucketblock"><h3><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/07/06/137219913/no-wheat-doesn-t-mean-no-noodles">'No Wheat' Doesn't Mean 'No Noodles'</a></h3><p>For people who eat gluten-free, Asian rice noodles are the crossover stars. But they're not alone.</p></div></div><div class="bucket img"><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/07/06/137176955/party-like-the-swedes-on-summer-solstice"><img src="http://media.npr.org/assets/img/2011/06/14/midsommaroverview_sq.jpg?t=1308090083&amp;s=11" alt="An American nod to &lt;em&gt;midsommar &lt;/em&gt;includes traditional foods plus a twist on a strong drink for toasting."/></a><div class="bucketblock"><h3><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/07/06/137176955/party-like-the-swedes-on-summer-solstice">Party Like The Swedes On Summer Solstice</a></h3><p>An American nod to <em>midsommar </em>includes traditional foods plus a twist on a strong drink for toasting.</p></div></div><div class="bucket img"><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/07/06/137034621/oh-the-things-you-can-do-with-a-farm-share-box"><img src="http://media.npr.org/assets/img/2011/06/07/csamain_sq.jpg?t=1307467182&amp;s=11" alt="Not sure what to do with that leafy bunch of ... whatever it is? These recipes will get you started."/></a><div class="bucketblock"><h3><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/07/06/137034621/oh-the-things-you-can-do-with-a-farm-share-box">Oh, The Things You Can Do With A Farm-Share Box</a></h3><p>Not sure what to do with that leafy bunch of ... whatever it is? These recipes will get you started.</p></div></div><div class="bucket img"><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/07/06/136824166/nuts-for-nutella"><img src="http://media.npr.org/assets/img/2011/05/31/nutellamain_sq.jpg?t=1306864888&amp;s=11" alt="The chocolaty spread elicits cheerful memories and sweet recipes from food writer Monica Bhide."/></a><div class="bucketblock"><h3><a href="http://www.npr.org/2011/07/06/136824166/nuts-for-nutella">Nuts For Nutella</a></h3><p>The chocolaty spread elicits cheerful memories and sweet recipes from food writer Monica Bhide.</p></div></div><p class="more"><a href="http://www.npr.org/series/kitchen-window/">more</a></p></div>

